T1  - The Effect of Options on Stock Prices: 1973 to 1995
AU  - Sorescu, Sorin M.
Y1  - 2000/02/01
PY  - 2000
DA  - 2000/02/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/0022-1082.00214
T2  - The Journal of Finance
